    "body": "Thanks for the suggestion. ERC721 enumerability is specified in the EIP, while ERC1155 enumerability isn't. Given the lack of a standard, and that ERC721 enumerability is a frequent source of discontent due to its gas overhead, I don't think ERC1155 enumerability is something we should include.",
